For the past 4 years I have had the great honor of serving female entrepreneurs through the @behindtherunwayexperience .

These women are passionate, prosperous, and persevering!

They literally have become a part of my why and the reason I keep pushing daily!

Being a woman is often difficult, but it’s so much easier when you have other women pushing you…

So, today…. We celebrate women around the world!

And just in case no one has told you lately…. SIS, YOU’RE DOING A GREAT JOB!!!!

#internationalwomensday

Every time I needed you and every time I didn’t know I needed you, you were there. I didn’t understand the sacrifices you made then in totality, but I understand them now. 

I never thought that I would have this beautiful opportunity to be there for you in this way. The talks, the laughs, reflecting, your prayers and to know that the “small” things you do like, putting my fav cup and coffee pod out for the next morning or washing my clothes and folding them, massaging my shoulders or the random, “come over here…let me pray with you”! …whew! 😩or the little things you do to show you care…means so much even though I don’t need you to do anything because you’ve already done so much. 

Mom, you’re one of a kind and I wouldn’t trade this time with you for anything. 

I love you. Thank you for loving me. ✨♥️

It’s okay to take YOUR time. Don’t let people, places or things rush you. Be authentically YOU! 

This top though…RESTOCKED!

I finally feel like, I’m getting back to myself again…

Last year was sooo busy with my personal life…moving into our new home, organizing and settling in with also moving our showroom…it was just ALOT…!!! 

…I’m finally settling down and feeling like I can breath…😩🙏🏽

Women, we do so much. We carry so much and sometimes we don’t realize we’re functioning and producing on fumes…take some time to breath…

Applying pressure is cool, but SLOW and STEADY wins too! To everything there is a season…

NOW…I’m ready to end the year strong.  I’m grateful for a fresh wind…

…now LET’S GET TO IT!!

When you know where you’ve come from you can’t help, but LIVE in gratitude and thanksgiving to GOD! 

I’m a southern girl from humble beginnings…Walmart & Cato’s were my favorite places to shop when growing up in Arkansas…

I can go in Walmart TA-DAY and put a number together BABY! …use what you got until God gives you more…

Hear me clearly, God will pull you from the back of the line all the way to the front of the line and won’t even say excuse me to those questioning whether you should be there or not! POWER BELONGS TO GOD! 

I’m learning to stop apologizing. Walk in it! Be an example. Be inspiration to others…let ‘em know that if God keeps doing it for me, he will absolutely do it for YOU! 

Stay humble. Stay true! As fast as God gives, he can take it away. 

Sit back, surrender and let the plan play out…

All that I have…I give it back to thee. 🙌🏽

God can do things you’ve never dreamed….thank you, father! 🙌🏽🙏🏽

Thank you, @thestellars for this beautiful opportunity. Wow! ♥️

Thank you to the Stellars Plus Team, Rhonda and Michelle for seeing me. For celebrating my gift. I so love and appreciate you both.

To my team…whew. Thank you guys for pushing me, ROCK’N with me and putting up with my nerves and me getting on top of yours…I pray nothing, but God’s continued BEST for you…♥️

Thank you to my runway beauties! Ya’ll have been there since day one!! Thank you for allowing me to share my gift with you! Thank you for supporting and showing up for me. Ya’ll are the real MVP’s. If it weren’t for you, I couldn’t do this. THANK YOU!!! ♥️

Lastly, thank you to my husband who is my biggest cheerleader. You allow me time away to build this brand and I thank you. Thank you for your patience. Thank you for pushing me and thank you for believing in me. I love you. ♥️

Whew chile, now I can take photos all day, but I’m tip toeing into these videos like NOW LISTEN!!! 😏

If I’m honest, I’m late in the game because of this crippling devil called fear…it will tie your two legs together and won’t have you moving AT ALL! 

I’ve decided that it ain’t gone be perfect and it ain’t gone be the best, but I’m going to give it all I got! 

Chile, punch fear in the nose and post the picture, start the business, write the book, start the podcast…your audience is waiting…Be authentic. Remain true. Just do you. 

People aren’t looking for perfection, they just want YOU…as I hit send…Pray for me as I pray for you! 😩🫶🏽

Moral of the story is…don’t let anyone make you feel small…shortly after that experience the staff of workers that used that supply room wanted me on their team…not just staff, but managers wanted me to manage their departments…NEVER SHRINK even when you feel like it…let the gift God gave you do the talking. 

Building a brand can be scary, but remember you have all the tools you need to succeed. Don’t let fear hold you back from creating something amazing. Trust in your abilities and take the plunge - you might surprise yourself with what you can achieve. You can create a brand that truly represents you and your vision with hard work, dedication, and a willingness to learn.

I did it scared and still do, so can you! LET’S GO!!

Transparent moment…

It takes me a minute to post after these beautiful styling encounters because I’m still trying to wrap my head around why God keeps presenting opportunities and opening doors…that quite frankly, I don’t ask him for…

God gently reminded me in the moment of me talking myself out of the assignment…he said, ”I don’t always call the qualified, but I do qualify the called.” I know the plans I have for you…😢

At the end of the day…whatever the assignment, whatever he has called me to, I want to hear him say WELL DONE!!! 🙏🏾

…for those of you, who like me, are trying to talk God out of choosing you, you can give it up, YOU’RE CHOSEN, because GOD CHOSE YOU! That’s it and that’s all! WALK IN IT! STOP APOLOGIZING for the things you didn’t ask for and let him do what he needs to do through you for those he has assigned to you!  All you need to do is SHOW UP…God will handle the rest. 

@kierrasheard for this beautiful opportunity to serve you this weekend. This past weekend was nothing short of amazing! Thank you for your obedience. Every part of the summit was planned and executed in excellence. You are beautiful both inside and out and your heart posture to be pleasing to God and towards the things of God, I’m certain touches the heart of God. ♥️
